metadata.name: Afronaut Fuel Cell AAC_002
metadata.description:
2 of 5 Afronaut Alliance Fuel Cells scattered throughout www.fromoville.com (MUST HAVE FUEL CELL 1 TO MINT)

Collect all 5 to help the USS FROmetheus on its rescue mission for Commander Buzz Ross & the other 11 Afronauts Lost in Space. #JUPITERBOUND “Others aim to Moon, we have our sight set on Jupiter.” ~ Commander Buzz Ross of the Afronaut Alliance HairForce One was Lost in Space on 3/26 Earth year 2021. On a quest to colonize Jupiter, Buzz left the HLHD Crew & slipped into a parallel universe & smart contract.
